Package: shian-ime
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: dbus, libdbus-1-3
Maintainer: Shian <shian@example.com>
Description: High-performance Input Method Engine for Linux
 Rust-IME is a high-performance input method engine written in Rust,
 providing excellent Chinese input experience with support for various
 input methods including Pinyin, Shuangpin, and more.
